VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)\bSELECT\s+[^\s]+\s+FROM\s+[^\s]+\s+WHERE\s+(username|password|apikey|token)=['"][^'"]+['"]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:example|sample|dummy|test|placeholder
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects hardcoded sensitive data in WHERE clauses of SQL queries, which can increase the risk of data exposure or compromise.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for SQL Query: Hardcoded Sensitive Information in WHERE Clauses.
